# rpi-lcd-i2c

HD44780-compatible I2C LCD driver for Raspberry Pi OS Bookworm.

## Features
- Works on Raspberry Pi 5
- Bookworm / Python 3.9+
- PCF8574 I2C backpacks
- Clean Linux (no MicroPython)

## Installation
```bash
pip install rpi_lcd_i2c

